Name: PowerUp Elevation
About the game: PowerUp Elevation is an cool little simple 'autorun' platform game set in a world full of crushing elevators and deadly traps. Avoid spikes, use gravity flip, pick up powerups and time your jumps well in increasingly challenging stages in order to steal a kiss from your mate before the 'death' time runs out. Features : Slower or faster gameplay mode. Two difficult settings/ two endings. 6 worlds, each world contains 8 levels + 1 practice level. You will be killed a LOT, so unlimited lives are enabled (but show time used). The game can been played a bit slower than normal for casual players with no penaty.
